        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Fall 2025 Golf Trends You'll Actually Want to Wear",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Fall golf isn't just about swapping short sleeves for sweaters, it's about making your style work harder. This season, the fairway fits are bolder, smarter, and way more wearable off the course. From the color everyone's talking about to retro pieces with major personality, TRENDYGOLF has the trends (and the outfits) to keep your game and your look sharp all season long.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
