    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Olive Green Everything",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Fall 2025 has spoken, and the verdict is in... olive green is the shade of the season. It's rich without being flashy, earthy without being dull, and it pairs with just about everything. Whether you're going full tonal or letting olive be the anchor to a bolder piece, this color screams fall energy. We're obsessed with how it looks layered on the course: think the Greyson Sequoia Full-Zip Hybrid Jacket in Forest over the Manors Golf Merino Wool Polo. The look is sharp, minimal effort, and perfect for transitioning from a chilly morning round to a casual afternoon in the big city.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
