    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Technical Layers with Streetwear Edge",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Fall golf means layering, but the key this season is mixing high-performance pieces with off-course wearability. We're talking water-resistant vests that look just as good over a hoodie as they do with a performance polo, jogger-style trousers you could wear to brunch, and lightweight outerwear that's more street style than sportswear. J.Lindeberg is leading the charge here, delivering sleek jackets like the Aerial Hybrid Vest that packs warmth without bulk. Style it over a TravisMathew performance hoodie and Malbon Utility Pants, then add a pair of G/FORE MG4+ shoes to tie it all together. The end result? A look that works for an 8 AM tee time and an 8 PM dinner reservation.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
