    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Takeaway",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Fall 2025 golf style is all about versatility, personality, and layering that works on and off the course. Olive green sets the tone for the season, retro details bring in the personality, and technical pieces make sure you're as comfortable as you are stylish. At TRENDYGOLF, we got every piece you need to nail these trends without overthinking it. Whether you're stepping up your course fits or just want gear that works with your day-to-day wardrobe, the site's got you covered. Now go layer up, mix it up, and play it cool this fall.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
